B. Cost of Rights-of-Way

The cost of rights-of-way, Table 68, includes only the land required for
the approach roadway and embankment and the toll plaza on the Anne
Arundel shore, and the approach roadway and embankment on the Kent
Island shore, located within the limits of the project, Sta. 8 + 23 to Sta.
346 + 95, as shown on “Plan and Profile,” Plate 67.

the work of construction of the bridge substructure into the following classi-
fications of construction work, with estimated quantities and at unit prices,
as listed in Table 69.
